Seabank Business Centre offers:
• Modern amenities – secure parking, 3 passenger lifts, airconditioned throughout, onsite café, contemporary ground level lobby, end of trip facilities, secure bike racks, kitchen and bathroom facilities on all levels and a garden breakout zone
• Quality refurbishment – recently upgraded lifts, ground level lobby, bathrooms and kitchen facilities
• Accessibility – under 5 min walk to 2 light rail stations, various arterial road access points and pedestrian/cycle ways leading into Southport CBD
• Ample parking – onsite parking for 250 vehicles across secure basement & on-grade carpark plus 2 hour free visitor podium parking. In addition, Council’s Carey Carpark (300 plus bays) is located directly opposite offering hourly, daily & monthly arrangements
• Flexible tenancy options - office tower suites from 54sqm* to whole floor of 544sqm*. Flexible floorplates with some turnkey opportunities available for immediate occupation. Shopfront suites from 54sqm*
• Unrivalled views – of Broadwater, Broadwater Parklands, Pacific Ocean, Surfers Paradise, Southport CBD and hinterland
• Quality tenant mix – existing ground level occupiers include café, dentist & financial services with major tower occupiers including Queensland Newspapers, State Government, Hays Recruitment, Arcadis, Aurecon along with a range of financial services, engineering groups and professional service firms

Secure your business’s future today – make the move to Seabank Business Centre, Southport’s premier office address.
